title: Saxony Landtag Election
view-if: year == 1923 and month == 2
new-page: true
tags: event
on-arrival: meck_schwe_election_seen += 1
priority: 2
on-display: {!  
    var cardEl = document.createElement('div');  
    cardEl.className = "face-figure2";  

    var image = new Image();  
    image.className = "face-img";  
    image.src = "img/states.png";  

    cardEl.appendChild(image);  
    var contentDiv = document.querySelector("#page #mid_panel #content");
    contentDiv.appendChild(cardEl);
!}

= Elections, [+ month : month +] [+ year +]

The Saxon state elections are to be held now.

# 1932 ref to dissolve saxony

- @meck_schwe: May we do our best...

